<a-modal
  title="批量上传文件"
  style="top: 20px;"
  :width="400"
  :afterClose="afterClose"

  v-model="visible"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
>
 <a-form-item
      label="Excel文件上传"
      :labelCol="labelCol"

  <a-upload name="file" :multiple="true" action="http://192.168.1.99:8080/faceManage/faceUpload" :headers="headers" @change="handleChange">
      <a-button>
      <a-icon type="upload" /> 点击上传
      </a-button>
  </a-upload>
 </a-form-item>
</a-modal>
